practitioner.about:
Dr. Jenan Abou Zour is a Specialist in Paediatrics at Medcare Medical Centre. She completed her Bachelor of Science (BSc) in Biology from the American University of Beirut, Lebanon. She obtained an MBBS and a Genral Paediatrics Subspeciality from the University of Balamand, St. Georges Hospital University Medical Center in Lebanon.

At the nascency of her career, Dr. Zour joined a Doctors Without Borders-affiliated hospital called Zahli in Lebanon as a Paediatrician. Simultaneously, she worked at a private clinic in Rashaya in Lebanon and subsequently moved to the UAE to join Medcare.

Dr. Zour’s expertise involves diagnosing, treating and managing medical conditions in infants, children and adolescents, growth and development monitoring, common childhood illnesses and preventive care. She supports new mothers with breastfeeding tips, general guidance, nutritional counselling, preventive medicine and vaccination schedules. She has successfully treated all types of acute and chronic illnesses, including respiratory infections like pneumonia, bronchiolitis, and asthma; acute gastroenteritis, dehydration, reflux disease, constipation, and severe and acute malnutrition; and neonatal conditions like jaundice and sepsis. She has proficiently treated measles, varicella, influenza, COVID, eczema, scabies, impetigo, severe dehydration and shock, status epilepticus and febrile seizures, and sepsis or meningitis. She manages long-term conditions, community health and congenital conditions through effective communication with speciality departments and physicians. 

She enjoys listening to music, singing and playing the piano in her spare time. She speaks English and Arabic.

locations.about:
Medcare Medical Centre in Damac Hills stands as a premium, advanced healthcare facility devoted to meeting the diverse healthcare needs of its community. This inviting medical centre prioritizes comfort and convenience, providing cutting-edge facilities and comprehensive medical services all under one roof. Ideal for patients of every age seeking precise diagnoses and prompt treatment across various specialties.

 

At the helm of Medcare Medical Centre Damac Hills is a team of multicultural, multilingual doctors, complemented by exceptionally-trained and experienced nurses and medical staff. The centre takes pride in its extensive array of state-of-the-art equipment, empowering its highly skilled medical team to deliver a premium level of care to all patients. 

 

Experience the warmth of family-centric care delivered by our highly talented medical and non-medical staff. At Medcare Medical Centre Damac Hills, we offer a range of services, including Internal Medicine, Gynaecology, Paediatrics, Dermatology & Aesthetics, ENT, Dentistry, General Medicine, Orthopaedics & Physiotherapy and Radiology.

 

As part of our commitment to accessible healthcare, Medcare operates a network of four hospitals and 20 plus multi-specialty clinics across Dubai and Sharjah. Our goal is to provide reliable and timely medical care to our diverse clientele.

 

Great News! We are expanding to better suit all your medical and beauty needs!
